posting_body: ['1162 82nd', 'St E Inver Grove Heights, MN 55077', 'Inver Grove Heights Rental Property 4825, 3BR+ Finished walkout basement', 'Beautiful, 3BR recently remodeled Rambler with Views of Lake Rosenberger.', 'This home won’t disappoint.', ' Only steps to be out on your dock, both a deck and a patio for relaxing & views.', ' Unit does have a fireplace however this is not to be used.', 'Main floor features:', 'Living room with built ins, NEW LVP flooring and NEW carpet throughout the home.', 'Kitchen with stainless appliances and white cabinets', 'Dining room with a walkout to the deck', 'Full bath', 'All three bedrooms on one floor with a .50 bath in owner suite.', 'Lower-level features:', 'HUGE family room as well as utility/laundry room', 'Walkout to a patio for a perfect evening of relaxing with lake views', 'Pets:', 'Open to dogs {2 max}-Deposit on one dog $500 on two dogs $750/ Monthly pet rent is $50 per dog.', 'Parking:', '2 Car attached', 'Utilities:', 'Tenant to pay for: Gas, electric, trash & water as well as cable & internet if desired.', 'Owner to pay for: Lawn care and snow removal.', 'Location:', 'Convenient to 55, South Robert Trail, restaurants, shopping, banking and more.', 'Schools: District 196 *** highly rated Rosemont – Apple Valley – Eagan School District', 'Application fee $60 per adult $65 for out of state applicants!', 'Call Brendan Ashton at', 'show contact info', 'OR Cheri Ludwig', 'show contact info', 'Realtors with Complete Management Services to schedule a showing.']
